Alt didn't make sure to fully understand the Bible, but chose the topics that were important to him and also mysterious.
"It wasn't an equal partnership," says Altepost: "This is about the pictures, the text just explains." A picture Bible was created.
For Hans Möhler from Luther Verlag, this work is an invitation to "deepen your life and find freedom".
